        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally within your melee reach is hit by an attack, you can see the attacker, and the ally gaining a +2 circumstance bonus to AC would turn the critical hit into a hit or the hit into a miss.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are wielding a single one-handed melee weapon and have your other hand or hands free.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You use your weapon to deflect the attack against your ally, granting a +2 circumstance bonus to their Armor Class against the triggering attack. This turns the triggering critical hit into a hit, or the triggering hit into a miss.</p>",
